WEBVTT

01:34.280 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:45.760 --> 01:46.600
Hello.

01:46.680 --> 01:47.560
Hello.

01:48.440 --> 01:50.080
I'd like to book a room.

01:51.520 --> 01:52.560
Thank you.

01:52.640 --> 01:55.000
- All guests must register.
- I'm not staying.

01:55.080 --> 01:57.360
There's one more room next door. Want it?

01:57.440 --> 01:59.320
I'm not staying. I'm just walking her up.

01:59.400 --> 02:02.040
This is just the usual trick
of you young guys these days.

02:02.120 --> 02:04.440
Rules state you must register.

02:05.400 --> 02:06.880
I can go up myself.

02:08.639 --> 02:10.560
Then, remember to lock your door tonight.

02:12.960 --> 02:14.360
Are you still practicing tonight?

02:14.960 --> 02:16.520
I'll probably go over a few moves.

02:17.120 --> 02:18.560
Don't stress. You got this.

02:18.640 --> 02:21.120
You're not the examiner. How do you know?

02:21.200 --> 02:23.680
I know a bit about the arts.

02:23.760 --> 02:25.360
- I think your dancing is--
- Hello.

02:25.880 --> 02:27.640
- Room 306.
- Thank you.

02:29.160 --> 02:30.160
I'm going up now.

02:32.160 --> 02:33.120
Thanks.

02:36.920 --> 02:38.720
Are you sure you don't want the room?

02:39.680 --> 02:40.720
No need. Thanks.

02:47.600 --> 02:48.720
Where are you going?

02:49.720 --> 02:50.640
To get a room.

02:51.160 --> 02:52.360
We're fully booked.

02:53.440 --> 02:54.600
Who are you?

02:55.120 --> 02:56.080
Front desk staff.

02:56.840 --> 03:00.000
- I'll pay extra.
- Even with extra, we're still full.

03:01.120 --> 03:03.040
See? The lights are off.

03:05.280 --> 03:06.400
Sorry.

03:07.000 --> 03:08.000
Try checking ahead.

03:31.040 --> 03:33.800
TO WEN SHUANGJIANG
JUST PICTURE THE EXAMINERS AS PUMPKINS

03:56.960 --> 03:58.880
Next up, scene performance.

03:59.560 --> 04:01.320
Candidate No. 7, Wen Yifan,

04:01.400 --> 04:02.240
please get ready.

04:37.920 --> 04:39.920
It's been a while
since you were this happy, right?

04:57.600 --> 04:58.720
3,143 DAYS

05:01.080 --> 05:02.680
I'm living happily now.

05:02.760 --> 05:04.560
I have my own family.

05:04.640 --> 05:07.520
Please stop looking for me.

05:08.680 --> 05:11.840
Auntie, if she doesn't want to see you,

05:12.880 --> 05:14.080
please don't look for her.

05:23.280 --> 05:24.800
Yuqing asked me

05:25.680 --> 05:26.520
to give this to you.

05:42.920 --> 05:43.800
This is ransom money

05:45.080 --> 05:47.400
to buy back her freedom?

05:47.920 --> 05:50.360
She hopes you'll start a new life too.

05:51.160 --> 05:52.360
Please, just let her go.

06:32.240 --> 06:33.200
Yifan.

06:34.400 --> 06:35.440
What's wrong?

06:35.520 --> 06:36.880
Need my help with something?

06:37.400 --> 06:38.320
No.

06:40.280 --> 06:41.200
Okay.

06:50.840 --> 06:51.680
Yifan.

06:54.040 --> 06:57.080
After you finish editing,
will you come to my welcome party?

06:59.840 --> 07:01.840
Not sure. I'll see how things go.

07:01.920 --> 07:03.360
But I really hope you will.

07:05.720 --> 07:08.640
Yifan. Still working? Everyone's left.

07:09.240 --> 07:11.920
Yeah, Yifan. You have to come
to our welcome party!

07:12.000 --> 07:13.640
Please!

07:13.720 --> 07:14.600
Come on.

07:14.680 --> 07:16.720
Su Tian is already there.
We're just waiting for you.

07:16.800 --> 07:17.960
Join us!

07:20.800 --> 07:22.640
Alright, I'll try once I'm done. Okay?

07:22.720 --> 07:24.400
Okay, we'll wait for you.

07:24.480 --> 07:25.440
- Let's go! Mu Chengyun, hurry!
- See you there.

07:25.520 --> 07:27.640
So, see you tonight.

07:48.840 --> 07:51.760
Look at you. Still thinking about sleep?

07:53.600 --> 07:55.480
Alright. Remember everything I said.

07:58.880 --> 07:59.840
Yifan.

08:01.480 --> 08:02.480
Mr. Gan.

08:03.040 --> 08:04.000
You're still here?

08:04.520 --> 08:05.560
I just finished a meeting with them.

08:05.640 --> 08:07.360
Come on. Let's go join the party.

08:07.440 --> 08:09.440
I'm skipping. I'm heading home first.

08:12.560 --> 08:13.400
Yifan.

08:17.880 --> 08:18.920
What's up?

08:20.000 --> 08:23.040
This place isn't like Yihe Daily, right?

08:26.640 --> 08:29.560
If anyone harasses you in any way,

08:29.640 --> 08:30.560
you have to tell me.

08:30.640 --> 08:31.560
I won't let them get away with it.

08:32.280 --> 08:33.280
No one has.

08:33.799 --> 08:35.039
Good.

08:35.120 --> 08:37.200
I was just worried.
You never join gatherings.

08:37.280 --> 08:39.039
Is there another reason?

08:39.720 --> 08:40.840
Really, no.

08:42.000 --> 08:44.400
Our colleagues here
are pretty easygoing, right?

08:45.640 --> 08:47.080
Everyone's nice.

08:47.160 --> 08:49.040
So, what's stopping you?

08:49.120 --> 08:51.120
Alright, go grab your bag.
I'll go get the car.

08:51.800 --> 08:52.960
Mr. Gan…

09:02.400 --> 09:05.080
OVERTIME

09:09.280 --> 09:10.880
Hello. We have a reservation.

09:12.400 --> 09:13.920
Miss Wen!

09:14.000 --> 09:15.080
Your friends are upstairs.

09:15.160 --> 09:16.160
I'll take you to them.

09:18.360 --> 09:19.360
You've been here before?

09:20.520 --> 09:21.440
This way.

09:25.600 --> 09:27.160
Just head up, and you'll see them.

09:27.240 --> 09:28.240
Thanks.

09:33.480 --> 09:34.400
Shot again.

09:35.560 --> 09:37.880
- Enjoying yourself?
- Mr. Gan!

09:37.960 --> 09:39.120
The boss is here!

09:39.200 --> 09:41.520
- Yifan.
- Take a seat!

09:43.520 --> 09:44.400
- Thanks.
- Let me get your bag.

09:44.480 --> 09:46.200
- No need. I can handle it.
- It's fine. Leave it there.

09:46.280 --> 09:47.440
- So…
- Thanks.

09:47.520 --> 09:49.000
Everyone,

09:49.520 --> 09:51.680
tonight, we're here mainly

09:51.760 --> 09:54.760
to welcome our two new colleagues.

09:54.840 --> 09:57.560
You two don't need to be nervous.

09:57.640 --> 09:59.640
Just treat this workplace like home.

09:59.720 --> 10:00.720
Also,

10:00.800 --> 10:02.560
everyone's been working hard.

10:03.080 --> 10:04.000
Tonight,

10:04.720 --> 10:05.960
drink up

10:06.040 --> 10:07.840
and eat up! It's on me!

10:09.480 --> 10:10.920
That's what we've been waiting for!

10:11.000 --> 10:12.520
Cheers!

10:14.600 --> 10:15.640
- Let's go!
- Thanks.

10:53.120 --> 10:55.000
Boss. Why bother coming over?

10:55.080 --> 10:56.800
You worked all day already.

10:56.880 --> 10:58.240
We got this. No need for you to worry.

10:58.320 --> 10:59.280
Not welcoming me?

10:59.360 --> 11:01.560
Boss, what do you want to drink?
I'll mix one for you.

11:01.640 --> 11:02.560
No drinking. I'm driving.

11:03.640 --> 11:05.680
By the way, your friends
are holding a party upstairs.

11:44.080 --> 11:45.480
Glad you came.

11:46.000 --> 11:49.560
May I stand on your left?

11:52.560 --> 11:53.520
Why?

11:54.200 --> 11:57.240
Because this way,
I'll be closer to your heart.

12:05.520 --> 12:09.040
Just think of it as a reward
for my hard work these days.

12:12.240 --> 12:13.120
Yifan.

12:13.200 --> 12:14.920
Where's that classmate of yours?
We didn't see him today.

12:15.000 --> 12:16.040
Who?

12:16.120 --> 12:17.320
The one who's…

12:17.960 --> 12:18.840
handsome and miserable.

12:18.920 --> 12:20.320
- Who?
- Here.

12:20.920 --> 12:22.520
Check out my idol.

12:24.040 --> 12:25.120
Look at him.

12:25.200 --> 12:26.760
Who stays this calm in a fire?

12:26.840 --> 12:28.400
Happy, I am very happy…

12:30.240 --> 12:31.640
Isn't that Senior Sang Yan?

12:31.720 --> 12:33.440
Senior?

12:33.520 --> 12:34.480
He's from our school, too?

12:34.560 --> 12:35.400
Yeah.

12:36.000 --> 12:38.160
He was in the same class
as another senior I'm close with.

12:38.240 --> 12:39.080
So, back then,

12:39.160 --> 12:40.760
I tagged along to their graduation dinner.

12:41.360 --> 12:43.520
After the dinner,

12:43.600 --> 12:45.400
did anything crazy happen?

12:45.480 --> 12:46.600
Not really.

12:46.680 --> 12:48.200
But I do remember one thing.

12:48.880 --> 12:50.480
At the graduation dinner,

12:50.560 --> 12:52.840
most people had a few drinks,

12:52.920 --> 12:56.120
except for two, the legends
of the Computer Science Department,

12:56.200 --> 12:58.400
Sang Yan and Duan Jiaxu.

12:59.000 --> 13:00.400
One didn't touch a drop,

13:00.480 --> 13:02.720
the other downed bottles like water,
over ten bottles.

13:02.800 --> 13:04.120
Ten bottles?

13:04.200 --> 13:05.160
Who drank them?

13:06.080 --> 13:07.360
Sang Yan.

13:28.000 --> 13:28.840
Are you okay?

13:32.560 --> 13:33.760
I'm fine.

13:33.840 --> 13:35.480
I'm just a little unsteady.

13:38.760 --> 13:39.880
Unsteady, huh?

13:41.120 --> 13:42.280
Let go.

13:44.680 --> 13:45.920
Let go.

13:47.000 --> 13:47.920
I'm talking to you.

13:55.280 --> 13:57.400
- Senior Sang Yan.
- Who's your senior?

13:57.480 --> 13:59.720
I'm a Nanwu University student,
too, you know.

13:59.800 --> 14:01.560
Could you be a little nicer to me?

14:02.920 --> 14:03.960
Wen Yifan.

14:05.800 --> 14:06.840
Can you stand still?

14:08.120 --> 14:09.920
Then do me a favor. Open the car door.

14:14.360 --> 14:16.000
Need help?

14:16.080 --> 14:17.160
- Yeah.
- No.

14:17.240 --> 14:19.440
You're clumsy and careless.

14:19.520 --> 14:21.400
You can't take care of my frail junior!

14:21.480 --> 14:22.960
Yifan, get in and sit next to me--

14:24.880 --> 14:26.000
I'm heading out.

14:28.000 --> 14:29.120
Take the front seat.

14:34.920 --> 14:35.840
Hurry up.

14:39.880 --> 14:41.080
Mind your foot.

14:51.520 --> 14:52.440
Where do you live?

14:53.840 --> 14:55.120
Nanwu University.

15:05.760 --> 15:06.600
- We're here.
- Wait in the car.

15:07.880 --> 15:09.280
Thanks.

15:10.560 --> 15:11.960
Get up.

15:15.680 --> 15:16.880
Senior Sang Yan,

15:16.960 --> 15:18.360
I can walk on my own.

15:18.440 --> 15:19.360
You're awake?

15:20.080 --> 15:21.760
Aren't you an actor?
That was terrible acting.

15:23.960 --> 15:24.800
What?

15:24.880 --> 15:26.040
I pulled

15:26.120 --> 15:27.320
that little trick ages ago.

15:27.400 --> 15:28.680
And you think it's your turn now?

15:31.280 --> 15:32.240
What are you waiting for?

15:33.800 --> 15:34.800
For me to carry you in?

15:42.640 --> 15:43.880
Stay safe.

15:53.800 --> 15:55.120
Is he feeling better?

15:56.120 --> 15:57.760
He's faking it. Can't you tell?

16:22.600 --> 16:23.600
You're leaving, too?

16:25.240 --> 16:27.840
The teacher finally
treated you guys to dinner.

16:28.880 --> 16:30.880
Didn't Su Hao'an say
you were going on a night tour?

16:31.560 --> 16:32.720
I'm not interested.

16:37.200 --> 16:39.160
Then I'll get going. Take care.

16:47.640 --> 16:48.800
What's wrong?

16:51.680 --> 16:53.320
I'm feeling a bit dizzy.

16:53.400 --> 16:54.280
Are you okay?

16:54.360 --> 16:56.160
I'm fine. Just…

16:56.240 --> 16:57.920
I'm a little… a little unsteady.

16:58.000 --> 16:58.840
If you could…

16:59.400 --> 17:00.480
give me a hand…

17:00.560 --> 17:02.640
that'd be great…

17:04.040 --> 17:05.720
Did you drink just now?

17:11.480 --> 17:13.160
Why would a high schooler drink?

17:13.760 --> 17:15.160
I thought it was juice.

17:15.240 --> 17:17.760
So, I just grabbed a cup.

17:17.839 --> 17:21.040
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine. Just go.

17:21.960 --> 17:22.800
Go on your way.

17:24.880 --> 17:25.720
Just go.

17:25.800 --> 17:28.480
Maybe sit down and sober up first?

17:30.000 --> 17:31.640
Sit here for a bit.

17:32.240 --> 17:34.440
Rest here for a while, okay?

17:34.520 --> 17:36.040
Yeah, I'm good.

17:36.560 --> 17:37.600
No worries.

17:38.440 --> 17:41.600
My dad can't handle alcohol.
Maybe I've inherited that…

17:50.200 --> 17:51.080
You sure you're fine?

17:55.520 --> 17:58.720
- Put some effort…
- Why are you so heavy?

18:00.040 --> 18:02.240
- One, two, three.
- One, two, three, go!

18:05.760 --> 18:07.080
- Are you feeling better?
- Yeah, I'm good.

18:07.680 --> 18:08.960
I'm still unsteady.

18:09.760 --> 18:12.360
Maybe put your shoulder under me?

18:12.440 --> 18:13.600
Isn't this the same?

18:13.680 --> 18:15.600
No, it's not stable. This…

18:17.040 --> 18:18.680
This…

18:19.200 --> 18:20.680
This position is kind of uncomfortable.

18:22.400 --> 18:23.520
Is this better?

18:33.720 --> 18:35.280
Alright, then just…

18:35.800 --> 18:36.920
Hold steady.

18:38.800 --> 18:40.160
This is much better.

18:42.040 --> 18:44.200
Take your time. No rush.
I'm not in a hurry.

18:45.120 --> 18:46.080
Does this work?

18:46.840 --> 18:48.800
- Is this comfortable?
- Yeah.

18:50.640 --> 18:52.840
STRAW HAT HOTPOT

18:56.760 --> 18:58.680
- What's so funny?
- Nothing.

18:58.760 --> 18:59.920
It's nothing.

19:05.200 --> 19:06.680
You were definitely smiling.

19:08.520 --> 19:09.640
Wen Shuangjiang.

19:11.040 --> 19:13.040
I think I messed up.

19:13.600 --> 19:14.640
What?

19:15.360 --> 19:17.240
Tonight…

19:17.320 --> 19:19.120
What I drank was really juice.

19:34.760 --> 19:36.320
No wonder you noticed.

19:37.000 --> 19:37.840
Noticed what?

19:41.840 --> 19:43.440
I'm telling you…

19:43.520 --> 19:46.600
I'm not usually like this…

20:14.200 --> 20:15.960
And this time, what's your excuse?

20:27.360 --> 20:29.200
Didn't you just say you could stand fine?

20:32.040 --> 20:32.880
I can.

20:34.040 --> 20:35.000
Can you?

20:46.400 --> 20:48.080
Wen Yifan.

20:49.320 --> 20:50.520
What?

21:02.880 --> 21:04.000
Are you trying to chase me?

21:05.120 --> 21:05.960
What?

21:06.040 --> 21:08.400
If that's the case,

21:08.480 --> 21:09.640
just be straightforward.

21:10.400 --> 21:12.480
Maybe… I'd consider it.

21:20.880 --> 21:22.320
Not at the moment.

21:22.400 --> 21:24.040
I'll let you know if I do.

21:51.440 --> 21:52.280
Where are we going?

21:55.920 --> 21:57.200
Sit down.

21:57.280 --> 21:58.240
Drunkard.

22:01.520 --> 22:03.120
Don't drink so much next time.

22:05.280 --> 22:07.840
At your graduation,
you drank over ten bottles.

22:07.920 --> 22:09.080
You're the real drunkard.

22:14.640 --> 22:15.480
How do you know?

22:26.400 --> 22:28.360
Why did you drink so much?

22:42.880 --> 22:44.000
Goodbye.

22:45.320 --> 22:46.360
Goodbye.

23:30.480 --> 23:31.360
It's been so long.

23:31.960 --> 23:33.080
I don't even remember anymore.

24:31.680 --> 24:32.920
Shuangjiang.

24:33.000 --> 24:33.960
Here.

24:34.040 --> 24:35.480
Drink this honey water.

24:35.560 --> 24:37.440
- I don't want to, Dad.
- Drink it.

24:37.520 --> 24:38.520
Come on. Be good.

24:39.040 --> 24:40.040
Here.

24:40.880 --> 24:42.520
It'll warm you up.

24:43.120 --> 24:44.800
Your hands and feet won't be cold.

25:01.080 --> 25:02.200
Drink it, then go to sleep.

25:25.840 --> 25:26.960
Thank you, Sang Yan.

25:28.600 --> 25:29.880
If…

25:30.520 --> 25:32.880
the renovation smell still lingers…

25:33.760 --> 25:35.400
you should stay here…

25:37.920 --> 25:39.560
for a little longer.

26:09.880 --> 26:12.880
Except for the two, legends
of the Computer Science Department,

26:12.960 --> 26:15.200
Sang Yan and Duan Jiaxu.

26:15.280 --> 26:16.480
One didn't touch a drop,

26:16.560 --> 26:18.480
the other downed bottles like water,
over ten bottles.

26:18.560 --> 26:19.840
Ten bottles?

26:19.920 --> 26:21.000
Who drank them?

26:21.960 --> 26:23.120
Sang Yan.

26:25.680 --> 26:28.240
But that night, he looked really off.

26:29.000 --> 26:31.640
He was drinking alone,
barely saying a word.

26:31.720 --> 26:32.880
He wouldn't listen to anyone.

26:35.600 --> 26:36.640
Sang Yan,

26:37.440 --> 26:39.640
was I really that bad to you?

27:15.920 --> 27:17.720
I'll treat you better from now on.

27:17.800 --> 27:18.880
Okay?

27:36.120 --> 27:37.000
Sleepwalking again?

27:49.600 --> 27:51.600
What triggers your sleepwalking?

27:53.920 --> 27:55.720
Even being drunk can trigger it?

28:01.840 --> 28:03.160
Just this once.

28:05.320 --> 28:07.320
Just one impulsive moment.

29:03.440 --> 29:04.920
Aren't you taking advantage
of me this time?

29:07.240 --> 29:08.240
Sang Yan.

29:09.120 --> 29:10.440
I really hate

29:11.920 --> 29:13.680
to meet you like this.

29:19.680 --> 29:21.480
I just wanted to do…

29:30.480 --> 29:33.320
what I really wanted to do back then.

30:03.640 --> 30:04.480
Alright.

30:05.120 --> 30:05.960
Let's get you home.

31:46.480 --> 31:48.120
That's all the time
you get to hug me tonight?

32:11.920 --> 32:13.520
What did I just do?

32:15.040 --> 32:17.320
Did I really pretend to sleepwalk?

32:18.600 --> 32:20.680
Did I really take advantage of him?

32:22.040 --> 32:24.000
How could I hug him?

32:24.520 --> 32:25.360
How could I hug him?

32:25.440 --> 32:26.280
I was drunk.

32:26.360 --> 32:27.480
Being drunk causes trouble.

32:27.560 --> 32:29.040
I'm never drinking again.

32:29.120 --> 32:31.640
Even if I do, I won't act recklessly.

32:31.720 --> 32:33.160
If I ever get the chance,

32:33.240 --> 32:35.200
I want to apologize to Sang Yan

32:35.280 --> 32:36.640
for what happened while I was drunk

32:36.720 --> 32:38.400
instead of carrying

32:38.480 --> 32:41.280
the blame for taking advantage of him.

32:41.800 --> 32:44.200
I can't let this guilt weigh on me.

32:46.240 --> 32:48.320
Sleep. Just sleep.
Everything will be fine tomorrow.

33:01.760 --> 33:03.040
I made some porridge.

33:21.160 --> 33:22.320
Last night,

33:22.400 --> 33:23.280
I think I sleepwalked again.

33:26.560 --> 33:27.840
I didn't do anything weird, right?

33:27.920 --> 33:29.200
You did.

33:29.920 --> 33:30.920
You just…

33:33.520 --> 33:34.360
hugged me for a moment.

33:37.680 --> 33:38.680
You were pretty restrained.

33:42.680 --> 33:43.800
Sorry.

33:47.440 --> 33:49.560
How many times has this happened? So,

33:49.640 --> 33:51.120
why are you feeling guilty now?

33:52.000 --> 33:53.960
- I mean…
- Weren't you pretty cocky before?

33:55.320 --> 33:58.440
Every time we talked about this,
you always had excuses,

33:58.520 --> 34:01.040
blaming it on being unconscious.
I'd say one thing, you'd argue back.

34:01.120 --> 34:03.400
And in the end,
you even tried to pay me off.

34:04.520 --> 34:05.680
Wasn't that you?

34:05.760 --> 34:07.040
How about this?

34:07.920 --> 34:10.040
From now on, just keep yourself

34:10.639 --> 34:12.120
locked in your room at night.

34:12.199 --> 34:13.040
Try not to come out.

34:13.960 --> 34:15.280
Do we have a beast at home?

34:24.920 --> 34:28.520
Lock your door.
I can't exactly break in, can I?

34:28.600 --> 34:30.960
Your sleepwalking is pretty unique.

34:32.199 --> 34:33.440
It even involves
taking advantage of people.

34:36.440 --> 34:37.639
I never…

34:38.159 --> 34:39.120
used to do that.

34:42.600 --> 34:43.719
I don't know why.

34:45.199 --> 34:46.400
So…

34:47.000 --> 34:48.239
it's just me you take advantage of?

34:50.960 --> 34:53.360
Or is this…

34:53.440 --> 34:55.000
some new trick of flirting?

34:57.200 --> 34:58.760
I'm starting to doubt you now.

35:03.240 --> 35:04.520
Was it really sleepwalking?

35:07.560 --> 35:08.600
Yes.

35:27.280 --> 35:28.520
Today,

35:30.360 --> 35:31.520
you're awfully quiet.

35:31.600 --> 35:32.440
Am I?

35:34.120 --> 35:37.400
Whenever we talk about this,
you usually have plenty of excuses.

35:40.880 --> 35:43.400
- But it's happened so many times.
- That's true.

35:43.480 --> 35:45.480
So now you just stay silent

35:46.120 --> 35:46.960
and accept your guilt?

35:49.040 --> 35:50.080
I'm full.

36:05.200 --> 36:06.040
Hey, beast.

36:26.840 --> 36:27.880
What?

36:28.440 --> 36:29.280
Press the first floor.

36:30.560 --> 36:32.040
I'm in a good mood today.

36:32.120 --> 36:33.720
I have a meeting near the TV station.

36:34.440 --> 36:35.360
I might as well give you a ride.

36:38.080 --> 36:39.280
Thanks.

36:47.680 --> 36:48.960
Not feeling well?

36:49.760 --> 36:50.760
No.

36:52.240 --> 36:54.360
Guess you burned
all your energy sleepwalking.

36:56.560 --> 36:58.280
Last night, when you lifted my shirt,

36:58.360 --> 37:00.720
- you were pretty enthusiastic.
- When did I lift your shirt?

37:00.800 --> 37:01.840
How do you know you didn't?

37:06.920 --> 37:08.800
Didn't you say that all I did…

37:08.880 --> 37:10.360
was hug you?

37:11.560 --> 37:13.520
Then maybe I got mixed up.
It must've been last time.

37:13.600 --> 37:15.200
It kept happening, after all.

37:15.280 --> 37:17.000
I can't remember them all.

37:19.200 --> 37:21.520
When I get time, I'll really go
get checked at the hospital.

37:25.960 --> 37:26.840
Sorry for the trouble.

37:30.960 --> 37:33.240
NANWU TV STATION

37:33.320 --> 37:34.440
Thanks.

37:36.880 --> 37:38.320
Be safe.

37:40.760 --> 37:41.800
Wen Yifan.

37:43.600 --> 37:45.720
You've… got something on your head.

37:46.960 --> 37:48.120
On my head?

37:49.600 --> 37:50.640
Left side.

37:51.520 --> 37:52.560
Isn't this the left?

37:54.000 --> 37:55.040
Right side.

37:59.160 --> 38:01.440
Back right. You can't see it?

38:03.160 --> 38:05.600
Come closer. Come closer.

38:24.240 --> 38:25.320
Alright, done.

38:27.000 --> 38:27.840
What was it?

38:29.240 --> 38:30.280
I have no idea.

38:32.000 --> 38:33.920
Quit stalling. We're in a hurry.

38:35.920 --> 38:36.880
Stay safe.

38:42.640 --> 38:44.000
- Morning, Yifan.
- Morning.

38:47.120 --> 38:48.160
Yifan.

38:48.880 --> 38:49.720
What's up?

38:49.800 --> 38:52.320
Are you dating…

38:52.400 --> 38:53.480
Sang Yan?

38:54.240 --> 38:55.360
No.

38:56.520 --> 38:59.400
But he drove you to work
and even patted your head.

38:59.480 --> 39:00.800
So, I thought…

39:02.200 --> 39:03.160
Alright, done.

39:05.080 --> 39:06.040
Did that count as patting?

39:06.640 --> 39:09.240
Miss Wen! Miss Wen, you have a package.

39:09.320 --> 39:10.160
- Mine?
- Yes.

39:10.760 --> 39:11.960
I'll get it.

39:13.560 --> 39:15.240
- Thanks.
- No problem.

39:15.320 --> 39:16.640
- Let's go.
- Is it heavy?

39:16.720 --> 39:17.720
Not really.

39:18.280 --> 39:19.520
- Thanks.
- No worries.

39:21.560 --> 39:23.560
- Is it easy to carry?
- Piece of cake.

39:25.320 --> 39:26.680
Morning, Fang Li.

39:26.760 --> 39:27.920
- Morning!
- Morning, Fang Li.

39:28.600 --> 39:29.640
Morning.

39:31.400 --> 39:32.520
Just leave it here.

39:32.600 --> 39:33.680
- Okay.
- Thanks.

39:33.760 --> 39:35.240
Look.

39:35.320 --> 39:36.600
What's up with those two?

39:36.680 --> 39:37.880
I have no idea.

39:37.960 --> 39:39.800
They always come and go together.

39:39.880 --> 39:41.720
Are they dating?

39:41.800 --> 39:42.800
What are they talking about?

39:43.680 --> 39:45.760
Anyway, if you need help, I'm here.

39:45.840 --> 39:46.920
Whatever you need.

39:49.040 --> 39:50.200
Thanks.

39:50.800 --> 39:51.880
Want me to make you a coffee?

39:51.960 --> 39:53.400
No need, really.

39:54.160 --> 39:55.840
It's fine. I wanted one anyway.

40:10.080 --> 40:10.720
DIAN, TRY USING THIS NEXT TIME YOU SLEEP
IT MIGHT STOP THE SLEEPWALKING

40:10.800 --> 40:14.000
Dian, try using this next time you sleep.

40:14.080 --> 40:16.240
It might stop the sleepwalking.

40:23.520 --> 40:24.480
Dian.

40:25.000 --> 40:28.120
I got the sleeping bag.
Isn't the package way too big?

40:28.200 --> 40:29.680
No need to thank me.

40:29.760 --> 40:31.360
I don't know if it'll work.

40:31.440 --> 40:32.520
But give it a shot.

40:32.600 --> 40:34.080
- Alright, bye.
- Okay.

40:46.360 --> 40:47.320
Yifan!

40:47.400 --> 40:48.960
You're finally back!

40:49.040 --> 40:49.880
What are you doing here?

40:51.440 --> 40:54.400
So, Su Tian said your roommate moved out.

40:55.080 --> 40:57.600
I want to move out of the dorms.

40:57.680 --> 41:00.440
So, I was hoping to check out
the place you're renting.

41:01.960 --> 41:03.200
That might not be a good idea.

41:06.400 --> 41:07.360
But I'm already here.

41:08.640 --> 41:10.080
I know it's sudden, but I promise

41:10.160 --> 41:11.480
I won't take up much of your time.

41:11.560 --> 41:12.560
But…

41:28.320 --> 41:29.480
Coming home late without a word?

41:35.160 --> 41:37.280
Why did you get off work so early today?

41:40.120 --> 41:41.280
Sorry for the intrusion, Senior Sang.

42:07.720 --> 42:09.440
NANWU TV STATION

42:09.520 --> 42:10.400
Thanks.

42:10.480 --> 42:14.760
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

42:16.120 --> 42:17.200
Wen Yifan.

42:18.920 --> 42:21.560
You've… got something on your head.
You can't see it.

42:22.520 --> 42:23.560
Come closer.

42:25.640 --> 42:26.480
Come closer.

42:41.240 --> 42:42.280
Alright, done.

42:42.800 --> 42:44.040
Stay safe.

42:47.600 --> 42:49.360
- Morning, Yifan.
- Morning.

45:48.600 --> 45:49.520
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

45:49.600 --> 45:50.640
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
